          About the Centers for Medicare & Medicaid Services (CMS)

                               Introducing CMS

   As of July 1, 2001, the Health Care Financing Administration (HCFA) is
     now the Centers for Medicare & Medicaid Services (CMS). Learn more
                        about what changes lie ahead.

